CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 27, 1945, pg. 4, reads: "Dies Suddenly - Little Karen Powell, year-old daughter of Mrs. Ruby Powell, of Bryn Mawr Road, was dead when her mother went to her room to see if she was covered. Her father is in Army. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Karen Powell standing on bench in front of light colored background, in Harris Studio
